This set of proxies is independent of any declaration i makes to its proxy (as the set explicitly excludes the at most one proxy (see Lemma 2) that i has prevented from holding an option), and each bid submitted by a proxy within this set is only a function of their own buyer"s declared  valuation (see Equation 1).
